* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji Emperor entered Edo Castle, renaming it “Tokyo Castle” and establishing the Imperial Palace.

