[[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:October 13 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:October 13 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[cdo:10 nguŏk 13 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:October 13 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:October 13 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[zh-min-nan:10 goe̍h 13 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:October 13 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:October 13 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[zh-yue:十月十三]] {{Lunisolar October}} '''October 13''' is the 13th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 27th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|97|ja|97|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ordered the young prince (later known as {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) to subdue the Kumano (熊襲). * {{ill|Genwa (Japan)|ja|元和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year (1623, December 4) – ({{placeholder: Great Martyrdom of Edo}} ) * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1804|ja|1804|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} achieved Japan’s first successful surgery using anesthesia.<ref>…</ref> * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji Emperor entered Edo Castle, renaming it “Tokyo Castle” and establishing the Imperial Palace.
== Births == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|709|ja|709|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 18|ja|11月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 49th emperor († {{ill|781|ja|781|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1231|ja|1231|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Tsuchimikado|ja|土御門天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 83rd emperor (* {{ill|1195|ja|1195|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1649|ja|1649|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 15|ja|11月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhiro|ja|近衛信尋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a court noble and regent (* {{ill|1599|ja|1599|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1841|ja|1841|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Watanabe Kasansan|ja|渡辺崋山|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Dutch studies scholar and painter (* {{ill|1793|ja|1793|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
