'''October 13''' is the 13th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events ==
* {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 27th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|97|ja|97|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 5|ja|11月5日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  ordered the young prince (later known as {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ) to subdue the Kumano (熊襲).
* {{ill|Genwa (Japan)|ja|元和|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year (1623, December 4) – ({{placeholder: Great Martyrdom of Edo|qq=}} )
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1804|ja|1804|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  achieved Japan’s first successful surgery using anesthesia.<ref>…</ref>
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji Emperor entered Edo Castle, renaming it “Tokyo Castle” and establishing the Imperial Palace.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|709|ja|709|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 18|ja|11月18日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 49th emperor († {{ill|781|ja|781|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛喜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1231|ja|1231|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 6|ja|11月6日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Tsuchimikado|ja|土御門天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 83rd emperor (* {{ill|1195|ja|1195|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1649|ja|1649|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 15|ja|11月15日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Konoe Nobuhiro|ja|近衛信尋|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , a court noble and regent (* {{ill|1599|ja|1599|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1841|ja|1841|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Watanabe Kasansan|ja|渡辺崋山|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Dutch studies scholar and painter (* {{ill|1793|ja|1793|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

