'''October 13''' is the 13th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|qq=}} .
== Events ==
* [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]] 27th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  [[:en:97|97]]  [[:en:November 5|November 5]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]]  ordered the young prince (later known as {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル}} ) to subdue the Kumano (熊襲).
* [[:en:Yuanhe|Genwa (Japan)]] 9th year (1623, December 4) – ({{placeholder: Great Martyrdom of Edo|qq=}} )
* [[:en:Bunka|Bunka (era)]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1804|ja|1804|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1804|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}}  [[:en:November 14|November 14]] ） – [[:en:Hanaoka Seishū|Kawaoka Seishū]]  achieved Japan’s first successful surgery using anesthesia.<ref>…</ref>
* [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}}  [[:en:November 26|November 26]] ） – The Meiji Emperor entered Edo Castle, renaming it “Tokyo Castle” and establishing the Imperial Palace.
